snippet.title: PAX West Trailer | Prehistoric Kingdom (Pre-Alpha)
snippet.description:
Prehistoric Kingdom is a zoo management game that gives players total control over the creation of their extinct animals and theme park.

- Wishlist the game! https://bit.ly/2Qg3myG
- Pre-purchase the game! https://bit.ly/2Nrgtz8
- Check out the latest news: https://bit.ly/345uMOa

Become the ultimate tycoon by taking charge of your very own prehistoric zoo; designing unique exhibits, hiring the required staff, and ensuring the safety of your guests. Choose from a wide roster of classic and lesser-known extinct creatures, each with their own detailed growth process and individual needs.

Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/prehistorickingdom
Twitter: https://twitter.com/PrehistoricK 
Discord: http://www.discord.gg/pkgame

Developed by Shadow Raven Studios. Published by Crytivo.
